courses.name: Introduction to Python Programming
courses.description: This course provides an introduction to programming with Python. Students will learn the basics of Python syntax and programming concepts such as variables, control structures, functions, and file I/O.

courses.name: Data Science Fundamentals
courses.description: This course provides an introduction to the field of data science. Students will learn basic statistics, data wrangling, data visualization, and machine learning techniques using Python.

courses.name: Web Development with React
courses.description: This course provides an introduction to web development using the React JavaScript library. Students will learn how to build interactive web applications using React components, state management, and routing.
